<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>QR Scanner Pro - Google Apps Script</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Lucide Icons CDN -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <!-- HTML5-QRCODE Library for Camera Scanning -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/html5-qrcode" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <style>
        /* Custom scanner animation */
        @keyframes scan {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(100%); }
        }
        .scan-line {
            animation: scan 2s linear infinite;
        }
        /* Hide scrollbars but keep functionality */
        .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .no-scrollbar {
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            scrollbar-width: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 min-h-screen transition-colors duration-200">

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center mb-8 gap-4 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="p-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30">
                    <i data-lucide="qr-code" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">QR Scanner Pro</h1>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Integrasi Google Apps Script & Sheets</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Connection Status -->
            <div id="connection-badge" class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-400">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                <span>Mode Simulasi (Lokal)</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Notification Banner (Custom, replaces alert) -->
        <div id="toast-container" class="fixed top-4 right-4 z-50 flex flex-col gap-2 pointer-events-none"></div>

        <!-- Main Navigation Tabs -->
        <div class="flex border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 mb-6 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar">
            <button onclick="switchTab('camera-tab')" id="btn-camera-tab" class="tab-btn px-4 py-2.5 font-medium text-sm border-b-2 border-indigo-600 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                <i data-lucide="camera" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Scan Kamera
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchTab('file-tab')" id="btn-file-tab" class="tab-btn px-4 py-2.5 font-medium text-sm border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-200 flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                <i data-lucide="image" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Scan File
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchTab('history-tab')" id="btn-history-tab" class="tab-btn px-4 py-2.5 font-medium text-sm border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-200 flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                <i data-lucide="history" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Riwayat <span id="history-badge" class="ml-1 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs">0</span>
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchTab('setup-tab')" id="btn-setup-tab" class="tab-btn px-4 py-2.5 font-medium text-sm border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-200 flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                <i data-lucide="settings" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Pengaturan & Script
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Contents Card -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6">
            
            <!-- Tab 1: CAMERA SCANNER -->
            <div id="camera-tab" class="tab-content block">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <!-- Scanner Container -->
                    <div class="relative w-full max-w-md aspect-square bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-indigo-500 shadow-inner flex items-center justify-center">
                        <!-- Camera Feed Element -->
                        <div id="interactive-scanner" class="w-full h-full"></div>
                        
                        <!-- Overlay overlay scanner target -->
                        <div id="scanner-overlay" class="absolute inset-0 border-8 border-slate-900/50 pointer-events-none flex flex-col justify-between items-center p-8 z-10">
                            <div class="w-full flex justify-between">
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 rounded-tl-md"></div>
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 border-t-4 border-r-4 border-indigo-400 rounded-tr-md"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative w-full h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-red-500 to-transparent scan-line"></div>
                            <div class="w-full flex justify-between">
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 border-b-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 rounded-bl-md"></div>
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 border-b-4 border-r-4 border-indigo-400 rounded-br-md"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Idle State screen -->
                        <div id="camera-idle-screen" class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center z-20">
                            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-indigo-400">
                                <i data-lucide="aperture" class="w-8 h-8 animate-spin-slow"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2 text-lg">Kamera Belum Aktif</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 max-w-xs mb-6">Izinkan akses kamera untuk memulai pemindaian QR Code secara real-time.</p>
                            <button onclick="startScanning()" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white rounded-xl font-medium shadow-md transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
                                <i data-lucide="play" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Mulai Kamera
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Camera Controls -->
                    <div class="w-full max-w-md mt-6 flex gap-4 justify-center">
                        <button id="btn-stop-camera" onclick="stopScanning()" class="hidden px-4 py-2.5 bg-red-100 hover:bg-red-200 text-red-700 dark:bg-red-950/30 dark:text-red-400 rounded-xl font-medium transition-all items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                            <i data-lucide="square" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Matikan Kamera
                        </button>
                        <button id="btn-toggle-torch" onclick="toggleFlash()" class="hidden px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 rounded-xl font-medium transition-all items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                            <i data-lucide="flashlight" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Senter
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Scan Results Box (Latest Scan) -->
                    <div id="latest-result-box" class="hidden w-full max-w-md mt-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-4 animate-fade-in">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 flex items-center gap-1">
                                <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Berhasil Dipindai
                            </span>
                            <span id="scan-time" class="text-xs text-slate-400">Baru Saja</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-sm font-semibold break-all text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 select-all mb-4" id="scanned-content">
                            -
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <button onclick="copyToClipboard(document.getElementById('scanned-content').innerText)" class="flex-1 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-xs font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
                                <i data-lucide="copy" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Salin Teks
                            </button>
                            <a id="btn-open-link" href="#" target="_blank" class="hidden flex-1 py-2 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950/30 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-400 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-900 text-xs font-medium hover:bg-indigo-100 dark:hover:bg-indigo-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
                                <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Buka Link
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Tab 2: SCAN FROM IMAGE FILE -->
            <div id="file-tab" class="tab-content hidden">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div class="w-full max-w-md">
                        <label for="qr-file-input" class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full h-64 border-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded-2xl cursor-pointer bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-850 transition-all p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-5 pb-6">
                                <div class="p-4 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950/40 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 rounded-full mb-4">
                                    <i data-lucide="upload-cloud" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Pilih atau Seret File Gambar</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">PNG, JPG, JPEG atau WEBP (Maksimal 5MB)</p>
                            </div>
                            <input id="qr-file-input" type="file" accept="image/*" class="hidden" onchange="scanFromFile(event)" />
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <!-- File Scan Result Box -->
                    <div id="file-result-box" class="hidden w-full max-w-md mt-6 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-4">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 flex items-center gap-1">
                                <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Berhasil Dipindai
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-sm font-semibold break-all text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-4" id="file-scanned-content">
                            -
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <button onclick="copyToClipboard(document.getElementById('file-scanned-content').innerText)" class="flex-1 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-xs font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
                                <i data-lucide="copy" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Salin
                            </button>
                            <a id="btn-file-open-link" href="#" target="_blank" class="hidden flex-1 py-2 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950/30 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-400 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-900 text-xs font-medium hover:bg-indigo-100 dark:hover:bg-indigo-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
                                <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Buka Link
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Tab 3: SCAN HISTORY -->
            <div id="history-tab" class="tab-content hidden">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Daftar Hasil Pemindaian</h3>
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                        <button onclick="exportHistoryToCSV()" class="px-3 py-1.5 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded-lg flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all">
                            <i data-lucide="download" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Ekspor CSV
                        </button>
                        <button onclick="clearHistory()" class="px-3 py-1.5 border border-red-200 text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50 dark:border-red-950 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:bg-red-950/30 text-xs font-semibold rounded-lg flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all">
                            <i data-lucide="trash-2" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Bersihkan
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Empty State -->
                <div id="history-empty" class="py-12 text-center text-slate-400 flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                        <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm">Belum ada riwayat pemindaian.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- History Table / List -->
                <div id="history-list-container" class="hidden overflow-x-auto max-h-96 no-scrollbar rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                    <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                        <thead>
                            <tr class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 font-semibold border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                                <th class="p-3 w-1/4">Tanggal & Waktu</th>
                                <th class="p-3 w-1/2">Hasil QR Code</th>
                                <th class="p-3 w-1/4 text-right">Aksi</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody id="history-table-body" class="divide-y divide-slate-100 dark:divide-slate-700 text-sm">
                            <!-- Populated by JS -->
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Tab 4: SETUP & INTEGRATION -->
            <div id="setup-tab" class="tab-content hidden">
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <!-- Google Sheets Configuration -->
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Konfigurasi Google Apps Script</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">Secara default, aplikasi berjalan di mode simulasi. Masukkan URL Apps Script Web App Anda untuk mulai menyimpan data langsung ke Google Sheets secara real-time.</p>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-3">
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-500 mb-1">Pilih Mode Koneksi</label>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                    <button id="mode-standalone-btn" onclick="setConnectionMode('standalone')" class="p-3 border rounded-xl text-left font-medium text-sm flex items-center gap-2 transition-all">
                                        <i data-lucide="globe" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Standalone Web App URL
                                    </button>
                                    <button id="mode-native-btn" onclick="setConnectionMode('native')" class="p-3 border rounded-xl text-left font-medium text-sm flex items-center gap-2 transition-all">
                                        <i data-lucide="cloud" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Native Apps Script Container
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div id="url-input-container">
                                <label for="gas-endpoint-url" class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-500 mb-1">Web App Deployment URL</label>
                                <div class="flex gap-2">
                                    <input id="gas-endpoint-url" type="url" placeholder="https://script.google.com/macros/s/.../exec" class="flex-1 px-4 py-2 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500" />
                                    <button onclick="saveEndpointURL()" class="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-medium rounded-xl text-sm transition-all flex items-center gap-1.5">
                                        <i data-lucide="save" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Simpan
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-1">Dapatkan URL ini setelah Anda mendeploy proyek Apps Script Anda sebagai Web App.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" />

                    <!-- Step by Step Setup Guide -->
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Panduan Langkah Demi Langkah</h3>
                        <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm list-decimal list-inside text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                            <li>Buat Google Spreadsheet baru, beri nama lembar aktif (Sheet) pertama Anda <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 text-red-500 font-mono rounded">ScanData</code>.</li>
                            <li>Klik menu <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-white">Ekstensi &gt; Apps Script</strong>.</li>
                            <li>Hapus semua kode di dalam file <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 font-mono rounded">Code.gs</code>, lalu salin dan tempel kode berikut:</li>
                        </ol>

                        <!-- Code block -->
                        <div class="relative mt-3">
                            <button onclick="copyAppsScriptCode()" class="absolute top-3 right-3 p
